    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E92 M3, featuring the high-revving S65B40 naturally aspirated V8 with its signature 8,400 RPM redline. This example is equipped with the 6-speed manual transmission and factory-spec Electronic Damper Control (EDC). Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including the replacement of rod bearings and throttle valve actuators to ensure long-term powertrain reliability. The chassis remains rigid with no signs of subframe fatigue, and the carbon fiber roof panel is free of delamination. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina consistent with a well-loved driver\u2019s car, the individual throttle bodies and VANOS system are in peak operating condition. An authentic, analog performance machine for the discerning enthusiast.",
