      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a well-maintained 2016 BMW M3 finished in Alpine White over Black Extended Merino leather. This vehicle has been a reliable daily driver and is in solid mechanical health. It comes with a comprehensive service history, including a recently completed 60,000-mile service that featured a fresh oil change, new spark plugs, and a brake fluid flush. The exterior retains a brilliant shine, though close inspection will reveal minor stone chips on the front bumper and hood consistent with highway driving. The interior is clean and smoke-free; the carbon fiber trim is free of cracks, and while the driver\u2019s seat bolster shows some light softening, the leather remains supple throughout. All electronics, including the Harman Kardon sound system and navigation, function perfectly. The car sits on factory 19-inch wheels wrapped in Michelin Pilot Sport 4S tires with approximately 70% tread remaining. This is an honest, turn-key performance sedan that balances daily usability with incredible power.",
